We ran down the stairs and it took us about ten minutes to get down from the fiftieth floor,” a resident of a skyscraper named George told Reuters.
According to the Dubai Civil Defense Authority, firefighters extinguished the fire at about 4:00 a.m. local time (00:00 GMT) and cooled the building.
