And sometimes they are killed, as apparently happened to photographer Ruben Espinosa, who was killed in 2015 along with four women in an apartment in Mexico three months after fleeing Veracruz.
Those who stay and continue to work balance risky decisions on a daily basis.
Ibarra - who once dreamed of being a poet - admits that he is afraid to write about the drug trade.
