As the organizers promise, the site will become an area of improvisation and a field for demonstrating new creative opportunities.
“The guests of the festival will be able to immerse themselves in the world of experimental media technologies and learn how innovations in science become a new tool for interaction with art”, – Elena Zelentsova, Vice President of the Skolkovo Foundation, described the focus of the forum.
Among the participants of Skolkovo Jazz Science 2017 there are many stars, including the Moscow Jazz Orchestra of Igor Butman, who will present a joint program with vocalist Yaroslava Simonova.
