Did PSG warn Barcelona of Neymar’s transition three years ago?
La Liga member may regret his interest in Marco Verratti
Paris Saint-Germain will not stop chasing Neymar after the club offered <0xC2><0xA3>189 million for his ransom, but did they warn Barcelona of a world record raid three years ago?
The sensational offer revived the summer transfer window when Ligue 1 was ready to break the world record for the cost of the transfer, more than double the previous mark associated with the return of Paul Pogba to Manchester United last season for 89 million pounds.
