Barcelona seems to have crossed that line when the Spanish club expressed interest in PSG midfielder Marco Verratti earlier this summer.
PSG has made it clear that it will not let the Italian national team player go under any conditions, and now it is likely that Barcelona feels the consequences of its offer in the form of the loss of one of its most valuable players, Neymar.
